  "title": "FOOD MANUFACTURING SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Job Duties</p>\n<p>1. Operate and maintain machinery.</p>\n<p>2. Do packing and product labeling and ensure accuracy.</p>\n<p>3. Monitor levels of stock and liaise with goods delivery driver and admin.</p>\n<p>4. Monitor and update stock levels in warehouse and keep strict traceability records of production.</p>\n<p>5. Maintain a flexible approach to work to meet team based work requirements.</p>\n<p>6. Observe and maintain safety levels with particular attention to machinery and electrical equipment.</p>\n<p>7. Undertake training to meet food legislation requirements.</p>\n<p>8. Maintain a strict level of personal and workplace hygiene.</p>\n<p>Requirement</p>\n<p>1. Team player</p>\n<p>2. Relavant working experience in food factory</p>\n<p>3. Might be required to work on PH and Weekends for overtime</p>",
